name: Monster High: Skultimate Roller Maze
overview: The monster madness goes underground in this roller-racing challenge where you'll skate through the catacombs beneath Monster High! The Skultimate Roller Maze is packed with monstrous obstacles and treacherous hazards waiting to send your hopes of victory to an early grave. Compete as your favorite Monster High character and choose your team. Get help from your teammates, using each character's special abilities and monstrous power-ups to flex your ghoul power and roll past your opponents. Multiple difficulty levels and a variety of gameplay options make sure each race is a scream!
